# Setting up Quay registry storage on Dell EMC Object Storage

## Adding TLS certs for Quay
### Add quay server cert in 'upload certificates' section
- Added del_ecs_ssl.cer
- use s3 in the beginning, e.g. s3.hostname.llnl.gov as the hostname

